reviewText: Good movies and a good value! All came stuffed in one case though and the last one is a different kind, but all in all good product.
Good product at a good price!
Good Scooby-Doo DVD set. You basically get four 70 minute movies, for the price of one.

Great value for the price I paid - four movies in one package. I did see from other reviewers that there was concern about the packaging (all 4 DVDs stack on top of each other) but we haven't had any issues. I usually pop all 4 out to let my grandson pick which one he wants. Great value for Scooby Doo lovers young and old :)

This collection is incorrectly identified by a number of reviewers as a collection movies.  The product description does not make it clear that they are not.  It's actually a collection of TV episodes.  I'm seeing the same reviews repeated on numerous products.  Is Amazon putting the same reviews on all the Scooby Doo DVDs?  As a collection of TV episodes it's ok, but when you're expecting movies, you feel cheated.
Four movies in one case! Great deal.
My son loves all of these movies they are great for travel we use them on the portable dvd player. He also enjoys watching them at home.
Scooby + kids = fun! All four are in the classic Scooby traditions, and are as fun for adults as they are for kids. And, there's no Ninjas, as well as no violence.

4 full length movies that keep my kindergarten age child occupied- for less than $10? This set wins my approval for value! And who doesn't love Scooby Doobie Doooooo!? This is one cartoon series that we can easily watch together and enjoy.

These are 4 full length movies. Well worth $10 in my opinion! They are 4 dvds stacked on top of each other (no dividers), but they stack pretty tight so they aren't getting scratched so far. I'm not a fan of the stacking discs, but these are stacked tight enough, so I don't mind. My two year old loves Scooby Doo, so we're happy! I would definitely recommend this foursome!

Great little bundle of movies for the kids. My only concern is that the DVD case comes with the 4 separate discs with each stacked right on top of each other. There are no dividers or separate holders for it so just beware. Not a huge issue but as the kid takes them in and out of the case I can see them getting scratched up easily or getting lost.

The movie set came well packaged and in good shape. It was everything as I had expected based on the product details. I love the product and will happily recommend it to others! This is a fair and honest recommendation - I am receiving nothing for writing. I thoroughly enjoy this purchase!
